mpionship|Championship]] |33||1||3||0||2||1||0||0||38||2 |- |[[2018–19 Reading F.C. season|2018–19]]<ref name="LB18">{{soccerbase season|55800|2018|accessdate=2 February 2019}}</ref> |[[EFL Championship|Championship]] |26||3||0||0||2||0||0||0||28||3 |- !colspan=2|Reading total !60!!4!!3!!0!!4!!1!!0!!0!!66!!5 |- |[[Cardiff City F.C.|Cardiff City]] |[[2018–19 Cardiff City F.C. season|2018–19]]<ref name="LB18"/> |[[Premier League]] |5||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||5||0 |- !colspan=3|Career Total !289!!25!!23!!6!!1!!1!!7!!2!!333!!31 |}
